		"body": "**Platform:** Mobile (Android)\r\n\r\n**Root Cause:**\r\nPlugins (like Backlinks) render their content through `NoteBodyViewer`. When a note had an empty body, the viewer was completely skipped due to a 2018 workaround (`!note.body.trim() ? null : <NoteBodyViewer />`). This prevented any plugin content from appearing on empty notes, while desktop worked correctly.\r\n\r\n**Solution:**\r\nRemoved the empty-body guard that prevented `NoteBodyViewer` from mounting in view mode. Now the viewer always renders when a note exists, allowing plugin content to display even on empty notes.\r\n\r\n**Changes:**\r\n\r\n1. **`packages/app-mobile/components/screens/Note/Note.tsx`**\r\n   - Removed `!note.body.trim() ? null :` condition\r\n   - Now always renders `<NoteBodyViewer />` in view mode when note exists\r\n\r\n2. **`packages/app-mobile/components/screens/Note/Note.test.tsx`**\r\n   - Added regression test: `should render the note viewer when the note body is empty`\r\n   - Ensures viewer mounts even with empty body\r\n\r\n**Test Plan:**\r\n- **Unit tests:** `yarn test components/screens/Note/Note.test.tsx --runInBand`\r\n  - All tests pass, including the new empty-body test\r\n  - No regressions in existing tests\r\n\r\n- **Manual verification:**\r\n  1. Install Backlinks plugin\r\n  2. Create Note A (empty body, only title)\r\n  3. Create Note B with content: `[[Note A]]`\r\n  4. Open Note A in view mode\r\n  5. **Result:** Backlinks section appears with link to Note B\r\n  6. Regular notes unchanged, edit mode unaffected\r\n\r\n**Platforms tested:**\r\n- Android (emulator) - Verified with Backlinks plugin showing content on empty notes\r\n- iOS (simulator) - Verified note renders without errors (plugin not tested as Backlinks not available on iOS)\r\n\r\n**AI Assistance Disclosure:**\r\nI used GPT (OpenAI) to understand the bug, plugin rendering flow, and to help with writing the regression test. All code was reviewed, understood, and manually verified by me.\r\n\r\n**Screenshots:**\r\n<img width=\"1080\" height=\"2424\" alt=\"Screenshot_1774460089\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fbbceed3-28bf-4cf9-8d9a-7f2282d354aa\" />\r\n<img width=\"1080\" height=\"2424\" alt=\"Screenshot_1774460092\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/223e799b-baad-4446-a2d4-be29b4c9e067\" />\r\n<img width=\"1080\" height=\"2424\" alt=\"Screenshot_1774460098\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6d659b9a-3129-4909-878a-936ca42acb5e\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n**Related:**\r\n- Desktop fix: commit 7ebfad1\r\n- Issue: #13456\r\n- Plugin issue: njobnz/joplin-plugin-easy-backlinks#5\r\n\r\nI have read and agree to the CLA. GitHub username: vignezkumaran",
